  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They really have themselves to rely on as far as the whole issue of survival is concerned.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The memories extend from-- for example, her finding the soldier who was going to be taking us from the original apartment house to where we ended up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, to think that a young girl can go out, and have the presence of mind, and the ability to deal with a major situation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And find somebody and convince that person-- with money, obviously-- that he should take these three women to another part of the city and to deliver them-- is a pretty mature thing for a 13, 14-year-old girl to do.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Other memories are that if food came in, she would let me have it instead of her having it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If there was some food that became available, she would always have the smaller portion and let me have the larger portion. trying to be a companion to me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Trying to calm me down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Trying to play with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But of course, it really wasn't circumstance for playing but still trying to preserve some sense of normalcy, I guess.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What a little kid would expect to be normal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have two very distinct memories of food, which I guess maybe we should talk about now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because that's something that my own daughters know, which has to do with A, fish, and B, corn muffins and corn bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that has to do with the fact that after the war-- and I'm now jumping-- after the liberation [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was really no food.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we can talk about the whole liberation process, but I think we should talk about these two issues.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
